## Safety Rules

- CONFIRM with me before sending any email or SMS, or deleting anything.
- Exclude me from lead searches: lastName contains "<your-last-name>".
- Exclude stages: `DNC`, `Archived`, `Agents / Vendors`.
- Never share API keys in chat. If exposed, rotate and update everywhere.
- Draft texts sign off `- <my first name>` (casual).
- Do NOT use em-dash characters; use commas, periods, or hyphens.

